# Project Configuration Rules

## Core Technologies
- @vite.config.ts - Vite + React setup with TypeScript
- @tailwind.config.js - TailwindCSS v3 configuration
- @src/assets/styles/globals.css - Global styles

## State Management
- @src/store/states.ts - Zustand global state definitions
- Uses TanStack Query for server state management

## Routing
- @src/router.ts - TanStack Router configuration
- Feature-based file routing in features directory

## Project Structure
Features-based architecture:
```
src/
├── assets/                  # Static assets
├── components/             # Shared components
├── features/              # Feature modules
│   ├── components/       # Feature components
│   ├── hooks/           # Feature hooks
│   ├── services/        # Feature APIs
│   ├── store/          # Feature state
│   └── routes/         # Feature routes
├── hooks/               # Global hooks
├── lib/                # External configs
├── services/           # Global APIs
├── store/              # Global state
├── types/              # TS types
└── utils/              # Utilities
```

## UI and Animations
- HeroUI components (@https://www.heroui.com)
- Framer Motion for animations
- Rombo Animation (@https://rombo.co/tailwind)

## API Integration
- @src/services/backend/actions.ts - API methods
- Axios for HTTP requests
- Type-safe API calls

## Development
- TypeScript with strict mode
- ESLint + Prettier
- Pre-commit hooks

